WEBVTT

00:02.921 --> 00:04.223
♪♪

00:04.229 --> 00:05.557
Mount Neverrest,

00:05.666 --> 00:07.452
the highest peak
in the world!

00:07.510 --> 00:09.533
Most prized
of the seven summits,

00:09.619 --> 00:12.096
Neverrest has claimed
the world's finest explorers.

00:12.182 --> 00:15.976
It is said to be
completely unclimbable!

00:16.178 --> 00:18.302
But now that smug stack
of stalagmites

00:18.372 --> 00:20.865
has to deal
with Scrooge McDuck!

00:20.923 --> 00:22.459
Okay, so instead
of spending Christmas

00:22.517 --> 00:24.601
in a billionaire's mansion
waiting for Santa Claus...

00:24.659 --> 00:26.607
That man is not allowed
in my home.

00:26.717 --> 00:27.939
He knows what he did.

00:28.016 --> 00:31.139
We're following an old man
up Mount Certain Doom here?

00:31.201 --> 00:34.584
Oh, Mount Neverrest is three times
deadlier than Mount Certain Doom.

00:34.723 --> 00:36.975
The mountain's summit
remains shrouded in mystery.

00:37.092 --> 00:38.596
No one's ever seen the top,

00:38.673 --> 00:40.490
which makes it
the perfect place

00:40.548 --> 00:43.771
to earn my Junior Woodchuck
Cartography Badge!

00:44.576 --> 00:46.318
Do you have any idea
how hard it is to find

00:46.376 --> 00:48.842
a topographical landscape
that hasn't already been mapped?

00:49.193 --> 00:51.703
- No?
- Well, very!

00:51.780 --> 00:53.951
I've got a geographic
information system,

00:54.028 --> 00:55.873
satellite radar detector,
thermal...

00:55.936 --> 00:58.652
Yeah, you don't need
all that fancy doohickory.

00:58.710 --> 01:01.162
All you need is your wits,
determination,

01:01.220 --> 01:04.232
and these,
my old surveying tools.

01:04.325 --> 01:09.801
Wow! They're rusty
with the wisdom of experience.

01:09.878 --> 01:11.170
That's the spirit!

01:11.279 --> 01:13.725
I'm gonna be
the first person to set foot

01:13.783 --> 01:15.318
on the top of Neverrest!

01:15.413 --> 01:20.217
And I'm gonna be the first
person to draw a picture of it!

01:20.410 --> 01:22.545
Ugh! This is
your captain speaking.

01:22.654 --> 01:24.053
Flight doors
are now open.

01:26.232 --> 01:28.740
Ah! Drink it in, kids.

01:28.817 --> 01:31.913
Her deadly peaks,
her bottomless crevasses,

01:31.990 --> 01:34.746
her flawless sheets
of brilliant white snow

01:34.823 --> 01:37.905
betray a new hint to the ancient
secrets hidden beneath,

01:37.982 --> 01:40.232
completely untrod by man!

01:40.305 --> 01:44.764
The untamed majesty
of Mount Neverrest!

01:52.474 --> 01:54.295
Ooh, churros!

01:55.924 --> 01:58.373
♪♪

01:58.444 --> 02:00.881
<i>♪ Life is like
a hurricane ♪</i>

02:00.982 --> 02:03.607
<i>♪ Here in Duckburg ♪</i>

02:03.694 --> 02:06.303
<i>♪ Race cars, lasers,
airplanes ♪</i>

02:06.366 --> 02:08.848
<i>♪ It's a duck-blur ♪</i>

02:08.907 --> 02:11.435
<i>♪ We might solve
a mystery ♪</i>

02:11.516 --> 02:14.060
<i>♪ Or rewrite history ♪</i>

02:14.170 --> 02:16.771
<i>♪ Ducktales, whoo-ooh ♪</i>

02:16.842 --> 02:20.428
<i>♪ Every day they're out there
making Ducktales ♪</i>

02:20.486 --> 02:21.873
<i>♪ Whoo-ooh ♪</i>

02:22.006 --> 02:23.729
<i>♪ Tales of derring-do ♪</i>

02:23.787 --> 02:25.654
<i>♪ Bad and good-luck tales ♪</i>

02:25.740 --> 02:27.561
<i>♪ Whoo-ooh ♪</i>

02:27.638 --> 02:30.217
<i>♪ D-d-danger lurks behind you ♪</i>

02:30.279 --> 02:32.500
<i>♪ There's a stranger
out to find you ♪</i>

02:32.558 --> 02:33.559
<i>♪ What to do? ♪</i>

02:33.617 --> 02:36.164
<i>♪ Just grab on
to some Ducktales ♪</i>

02:36.252 --> 02:37.467
<i>♪ Whoo-ooh ♪</i>

02:37.525 --> 02:39.476
<i>♪ Every day they're out there ♪</i>

02:39.584 --> 02:41.406
<i>♪ Making Ducktales ♪</i>

02:41.464 --> 02:42.912
<i>♪ Whoo-ooh ♪</i>

02:42.976 --> 02:45.328
<i>♪ Tales of daring
bad and good ♪</i>

02:45.416 --> 02:48.059
<i>♪ Not phony tales
or cottontails ♪</i>

02:48.117 --> 02:49.548
<i>♪ No, Ducktales! ♪</i>

02:49.606 --> 02:52.843
<i>♪ Whoo-ooh! ♪</i>
